                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "eed12dca-971e-4c67-86b1-f37264931efe",
                                                    "actorId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                                    "amount": "1",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "9bc0db51-b220-4480-b3d8-7e7f22b2d8f4",
                                                    "actorId": "bdddd1b1-bbf3-4dd5-bbd6-0ef3115d8b66",
                                                    "amount": "1",
                                                    "change": "0",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "bce6420f-e268-4505-ace8-0f802b8354b6",
                                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "You must have 'bats in the belfry' if you think that is the correct answer, Herr O'Conner.",
                                                    "emotion": "3",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "5",
                                            "ExitMenu": true
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": false
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "1b305c16-7d76-420c-9754-4a725765c997",
                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "8421f0b8-05eb-48e3-b0b4-71131e961b28",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Bats explore their environment through the use of sound. They listen to everything around them and use that information to maneuver.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "40c82c3a-b6f3-4f97-866b-a00d080620ee",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "So, too, do Rogues. At night, your ears are often better than your eyes at recognizing danger. That's why Rogues listen first and then act. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d7038c58-2022-42b4-b819-ff80de825e9d",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Perception is a critical skill for social situations. You can learn a great deal by what others say, particularly when they don't know you are listening. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.addJournalEntry",
                                    "id": "24b1ec65-d4b8-4062-8dbe-9d67585309ea",
                                    "name": "Batty Lesson",
                                    "notify": true,
                                    "description": "A whole lecture on listening at doors. Fledermaus sounds like something my mom would do at the sight of a rodent. We're supposed to eavesdrop at the flop of a bat... Time to brush up on my \"over-earing\" skills."
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "568e88f8-28e0-4462-9034-13de9ebeff5d",
                                    "scriptId": "b200ef65-81a0-4f26-ab13-0f2a0f2b351e",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "45184025-f6cd-454c-8be6-69896a6adf4b",
                                    "actorId": "2ae7a408-9338-4b78-af6b-ba7a28e050ac",
                                    "actorId2": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "text": "We get excellent practice for our listening skills in this class because you, sir, always say such important and interesting things.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "6f8b3c20-2ad5-46c7-9f15-b2f49641adff",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": "2ae7a408-9338-4b78-af6b-ba7a28e050ac",
                                    "text": "I hope that all of you listen as carefully as Herr Sosi.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.invokeScript",
                                    "id": "f431add1-78c3-4634-a757-2f1808c78313",
                                    "scriptId": "63b3052c-fb12-4a29-b7db-17ee01dbdae1",
                                    "entryPointId": "",
                                    "currentScope": "Scenes",
                                    "currentSceneId": "ea6c0ba0-0d23-4c0d-80ed-b8611588a665",
                                    "currentActorId": null,
                                    "currentStoryEventId": null,
                                    "currentPropId": null
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1332f3bd-e7b9-4032-bc1a-3a1fef71402b",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Your assignment for the rest of today is to practice the 'Way of the Fledermaus' and use your listening skills. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.quests",
                                    "id": "04fa4144-e571-4225-b661-3cd2258bc13a",
                                    "sceneId": "e8520824-d970-4c6e-8aec-6c308c8846ab",
                                    "propId": "4f28916c-840b-4cbc-b0c6-b7acffbd3802",
                                    "target": "0",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "b7377b4b-c4b5-408c-bac1-5605f1e10b87",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Be aware of noise and its source. Sound can be your first warning of oncoming danger.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "1f328d4a-2079-43c3-90c6-dd729c5b8f98",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Evening is an ideal time for listening at doors. People are more likely to gather for conversations at that time.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "9e1c55f5-2072-4328-ad40-804eefd887be",
                                    "actorId": "b7cbd02d-8e2f-4a8d-99a7-02b132d86e1d",
                                    "actorId2": null,
                                    "text": "Try not to be too obvious about it, particularly when you are listening at doors. Keep in mind rule number six - don't get caught!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "c101d9b8-298c-4b6f-87ab-d11177a39afe",
                                    "type": "nodes.improveSkill",
                                    "skill": "Perception",
                                    "amount": "5",
                                    "notify": true
